Package org.rapla.client

The client package is responsible for initialize the gui and the client-plugins and providing the services for the client application.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClientExtension
    classes implementing ClientExtension are started automaticaly when a user has successfully login into the Rapla system.
    ClientService
    This service starts and manages the rapla-gui-client.
    ClientServiceContainer  
    RaplaClientExtensionPoints
    Constant Pool of basic extension points of the Rapla client.
    RaplaClientListener  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MainApplet
    The applet-encapsulation of the Main.class reads the configuration from the document-base of the applet and displays an applet with a start button.
    MainWebclient  
    MainWebstart  
    RaplaClientListenerAdapter
